team.name: Guardians For Guardians

blocks.text: Guardians For Guardians are a thriving Destiny centric, multi platform community catering to players of all abilities.
Community elected council members ensure that G4G is shaped by the community for the community and that no one is left excluded.

Always actively recruiting, we run a range of different events each week including raids for beginners right through to advanced speed runs, general PVP to Trials and Competitive and special events, all are welcome to join and participate.
